Looking for a Ford Mustang near Washington?

The Ford Mustang is available as a fastback or as convertible, with one of four engines. The base engine is an EcoBoost 2.3L turbocharged 4-cylinder. More powerful Mustang GT variants are powered by a 5.0L V8. The top-of-the-line engine is a 5.2L V8 powering GT350 models. With the largest selection of cars from dealers and private sellers, Autotrader can help find the perfect Mustang for you.

Autotrader has 2,852 Ford Mustangs for sale near Washington, DC, including a Certified 2015 Ford Mustang GT Convertible, a Certified 2015 Ford Mustang GT Coupe, and a Used 2011 Ford Mustang Convertible.

Not sure if a Mustang is the right fit for you?

That's okay! We make it easy to shop for your next vehicle by body type, mileage, price, and much more.You can find other popular Ford vehicles such as F150, F250, and Explorer on Autotrader.
